Goal:
Test software interrupt MSIP.

Details:
t1: Will loop, waiting for FCC and trigger MSIP for t0;
t0: Will increment FCC for t1, then loop waiting for interrupts to be triggered
    while doing ld/sd, csr stall or spinlock. Once the interrupt is received, it 
    will increment FCC for t1 so that it can trigger the next one.


